      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Like the concept, the production TRX will likely become the most powerful Ram 1500 ever built with some version of the Hellcat V8, and it's expected that this truck will also be available with the Ram's more basic 5.7-liter Hemi V8 and the 3.6-liter V6. The highlight of this truck, of course, will be the performance-tuned off-road components such as a wider track, beefed up suspension, stronger axles and likely a 4x4 performance control system with a Baja mode.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
