            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "There is less than a week until we find out all of the details about the 2021 Ram 1500 TRX. The official reveal will be streamed on Ram's YouTube and Facebook pages, so if you like ",
